Please note, after canceling your account:

You will no longer be able to use this account to play the game;
You will not be able to recover the account, and any rights associated with the account will be automatically forfeited;
We will no longer retain any of your information or will anonymize your data;
This includes account information, game logs, game equipment, and any other data generated from using this game service;
Any accounts associated with this account in other games will also be canceled;
Your account information on other clients will also be canceled.
